{"body": "I recently needed this for spatial queries, but it's also needed when ordering by parameterized subqueries:\n\n```ruby\nclass Player < ActiveRecord::Base\n  # Usage: Player.report_top_active_players(7.days.ago).limit(5)\n  def report_top_active_players since = 5.days.ago\n    num_games_created = <<-SQL\n      ( SELECT COUNT(*) \n        FROM players p \n          INNER JOIN games g ON g.created_by_id = p.id \n        WHERE p.id = players.id \n          AND g.created_at > ? )\n      DESC\n    SQL\n\n    order([num_games_created, since])\n  end\nend\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6696327", "created_at": "2012-07-01T19:44:07Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5949#issuecomment-6696327", "updated_at": "2012-07-01T19:44:07Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5949, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/mildmojo", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/4434b43feab44b18147100a8a31165c1?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F5914006c331f63ee1903b9ab6b55c3ad.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo/received_events", "gravatar_id": "4434b43feab44b18147100a8a31165c1", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "mildmojo", "type": "User", "id": 103495, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mildmojo/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523810febd3543c15100d73d"}, "id": 6696327, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5949"}
